name: Emma Johnson
bio: Emma is a passionate senior at ACU pursuing a degree in Business Administration. As President of Alpha Company, she has demonstrated exceptional leadership skills and a commitment to service. Emma enjoys playing intramural sports, particularly basketball, and maintains an impressive academic record. Originally from Austin, Texas, she hopes to pursue a career in corporate leadership after graduation.

In his free time, he enjoys coding, playing chess, and mentoring younger students in programming.
